org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFWidgetStyle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EEFButtonStyle, EEFCheckboxStyle, EEFCustomWidgetStyle, EEFHyperlinkStyle, EEFLabelStyle, EEFListStyle, EEFRadioStyle, EEFSelectStyle, EEFTextStyle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFButtonStyleImpl, EEFCheckboxStyleImpl, EEFCustomWidgetStyleImpl, EEFHyperlinkStyleImpl, EEFLabelStyleImpl, EEFListStyleImpl, EEFRadioStyleImpl, EEFSelectStyleImpl, EEFTextStyleImpl, EEFWidgetStyleImpl

    public interface EEFWidgetStyle
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Widget Style'. Represents a style that can be applied on widgets.

    The following features are supported:

    • Label Background Color Expression
    • Label Foreground Color Expression
    • Label Font Name Expression
    • Label Font Size Expression
    • Label Font Style Expression
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFWidgetStyle()

        java.lang.String getLabelBackgroundColorExpression()
        Returns the value of the 'Label Background Color Expression' attribute. Defines the background color of the widget. It must be defined as hex (#000000) or RGB (rgb(0,0,0)).
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Label Background Color Expression' attribute.
